              <i class="fas fa-leaf mr-1"></i> Catnip Critter Collection
            </span>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              "As a discerning feline, I rarely approve of human-made toys. But these catnip critters? Purr-fect! The texture mimics real prey, and I've been proudly displaying my collection on the couch. My humans are pleased too! üêæ"
